Name: Chain lightning

Object: /d/Sparkle/guilds/arcane/spells/chain_lightning.c

Cost: 

Skills: 

Description: Tier 2 spell
                 Targets: variable, unspecified defaults to current enemy
		             (if currently in combat)
		 Slightly different from the basic attack spell. If cast on a
		 specified target to initiate combat, will damage that one
		 target. If cast in combat, will minimally damage all enemies
		 currently attacking the caster (hence the keyword 'chain').
		 
Requirements: 
    SS_ELEMENT_FIRE     
    SS_FORM_DIVINATION      
    poison ivy